# Lam quen ung dung don gian su dung flutter va dart

phat trien ung dung full-stack
flutter la cong cu de phat trien ung dung web , ung dung di dong (Android,IOS) , giup ta
viet 1 lan va co the chay tren nhieu nen tang khac nhau

# Muc tieu

-hieu va ap dung cac khai niem co ban ve ung dung web dong, ung dung da nen tang
-su dung dart va thu vien shelf, shelf_router de tao server don gian, xu ky cac yeu cau HTTP theo chuan RESTFUL API

# Cac buoc thuc hien

# 1. khoi tao du an

- tao 2 folder frontend va backend

# 2. tao code backend

```bash
- cd backend
```

```bash
- dart create -t server-shelf . --force
```

# 3. tao code frontend

```bash
- cd frontend
```

```bash
- flutter create -e .
```

# 4. Them thu vien http

```bash
- flutter pub add http
```

# 5. Thiet lap debug cho ca backend va frontend

- mo main.dart
- cho `run and debug` va `create a launch`
